Project management in Emacs.  Managing groups of files together, especially code.

== Full Project Management Libraries ==

These libraries have the goal to be full project-management solutions.

* [https://github.com/bbatsov/projectile projectile]
* [http://wiki.github.com/jrockway/eproject eproject]
* a different library named [[eproject]]
* [http://cedet.sourceforge.net/projects.shtml CEDET]
* [[project-buffer-mode.el]]
* [[mk-project.el]]

== Project Helpers or Simplified Project Libraries ==

These libraries address some aspect of project management without being complete solutions.

* [https://github.com/eglaysher/find-things-fast find-things-fast]
* desktop.el (included with Emacs)
* FindFileInProject
* ProjectLocalVariables
* MinimalSessionSaver

